Cell["\<\
The first cell of this notebook automatically inputs the current weather data \
from a personal weather station into the Wolfram Blockchain and a Databin. \
Use the cell below to have this task executed once per hour using CloudDeploy \
and ScheduledTask. Enter your own MyAcuRite email and password along with the \
name of your own Databin.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.771070855795401*^9, 3.7710709002616243`*^9}, {
   3.771082948212419*^9, 3.771082954403407*^9}, {3.7710843093850603`*^9, 
   3.771084313003523*^9}, {3.77108524061522*^9, 3.7710853136265383`*^9}, {
   3.771150412019314*^9, 3.771150436640399*^9}, {3.7711528496053457`*^9, 
